data.description: A nice 3 bedroom 1 and 1/2 bath home sitting on a nice lot on a dead end street. The home has a large kitchen with great storage and room for family to sit and enjoy dinner. The first floor has dining room space and a large living room with an enclosed porch with laundry room and a half bath for your convenience. The upstairs has 3 bedrooms and a full bath. The basement makes a great area for storage and a possible area for a workbench for all your tools. The 2 stall garage adds room for outside storage of lawn equipment and other outside tools. The home will make a nice starter or possible investment opportunity.
